text: Kaikohe is an inland town in the Far North District, New Zealand. It is situated 260 kilometers from Auckland and 85 kilometers from WhangƒÅrei. It has two state highways running through the town State Highway 12 and State Highway 15 running through the town. It has 6 schools including Northland College in the town and former prime minister David Lange was once a resident. ==References== Category:Towns in Northland Region Category:Far North District Category:Hokianga
